This is the combined ChangeLog for pxlib and pxview, started in September 2015.

Prior to this, each project had their own ChangeLog, which are still in
their respective directories.

pxlibview v0.5:
        - Slurped in pxlib v0.6.3 and pxview 0.2.5
        - Modernized the GNU Autotools usage
        - Combined them into a single package
        - Fixed a few bugs.
